After months of administrative hell, 45 000$ of adoption fees and a total of 4 trips out there, they finally came back with 3 children. Back then, they were 2, 5 and 8.  It was not as hard as they expected regarding the adaptation but when they reached puberty, things got ugly. Only one of them in doing ok now, the other ones are not even talking to there (adoptive) parents...
